name: Fashion Hueshin
description: Fashion Hueshin The Fashion Hueshin show is an ironic statement about fashion. The concept of labor (in particular construction) as an act of creativity is touched upon.  Another subtext of the collection is revealed in the names and images, where the models are the electorate, and the fashion designer is the government class, which sets the style of clothing by its laws and economic situation. By Vlas Belov Website: http://vlasbelov.tilda.ws/ MP4 1080x1080 Music: W.k. «Marmelada»
